{"tid":234504,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[求救]xbox one手制問題（有圖）","createTime":"2017-05-08T10:58:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-08T17:46:13.000Z","uid":74380,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d6bc3a87394684c7dbcb2a34cee2b5da436c2172","tid":234504,"uid":74380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T10:58:28.000Z","msg":"今日買左個xbox one手制連埋個wireless<br />\n呢隻：<img src=\"https://holland.pk/sij1ctum\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fsij1ctum&h=ec6d18a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n諗住連落部電腦度打機,說明書就話插左個wireless落電腦再禁粒制之後禁埋xbox one粒制就ok<br />\n廢時1999都係比返張圖：<img src=\"https://holland.pk/n5o82jap\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fn5o82jap&h=f492962f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n如是者就跟住張圖咁做,但結果禁完個wireless個燈就閃緊,但個手制就乜燈都冇閃,而家detect唔撚到個手制用唔到,有冇巴打識搞幫幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />上網搵都搵唔到點樣解決<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申win10"},{"pid":"158ff299a809e31f50d7dd0b72f83d0634fba06f","tid":234504,"uid":57811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T11:03:11.000Z","msg":"手制無電?未裝driver?"},{"pid":"3fd5ad2a011365cbeefeac6f55e90521e7ba235d","tid":234504,"uid":74380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T11:09:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>手制無電?未裝driver?</blockquote><br />\n個盒入面有電比,driver就應該裝左"},{"pid":"534eab42dffc3042e013f63e7cccc6c5d84dd250","tid":234504,"uid":74380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T11:16:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>手制無電?未裝driver?</blockquote><br />\n個盒入面有電比,driver就應該裝左</blockquote><br />\n因為我用usb線連手制既話係可以用到"},{"pid":"9e3499118604074bd69dd24c856bd77aee262af3","tid":234504,"uid":74380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T11:30:27.000Z","msg":"幫幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5b84cc53445bd49545ee3f31da0b7ec13cef810","tid":234504,"uid":54305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T11:56:34.000Z","msg":"你隻手掣連咗落隻蛋到未呀？<br />\n手掣個頂有粒好細嘅掣，<br />\n先按隻蛋嘅掣，再按手掣頂上粒掣，之後就對得到。"},{"pid":"4e74bfb59bfefeb220a7a3eaa399ccf1edf9ed7c","tid":234504,"uid":93503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T12:10:21.000Z","msg":"要上ms個網dl返個手掣driver，我都用緊呢隻"},{"pid":"2b652655cf0cc94fd13c62eae23654d604e7bc0d","tid":234504,"uid":74380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T13:47:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你隻手掣連咗落隻蛋到未呀？<br />\n手掣個頂有粒好細嘅掣，<br />\n先按隻蛋嘅掣，再按手掣頂上粒掣，之後就對得到。</blockquote><br />\n我就係咁做,但個手制禁極都冇燈閃"},{"pid":"a2f2ba4e04fa95dcc8470ff87b0b5f48a71331e2","tid":234504,"uid":74380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T13:48:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>要上ms個網dl返個手掣driver，我都用緊呢隻</blockquote><br />\n已經搞左成日down左一堆野都仲係唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc52c1040158244739a2039bcb5efe873b0a52d5","tid":234504,"uid":376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T13:51:25.000Z","msg":"做咩唔買xbox one s果隻<br />\n果隻可以用藍牙連接"},{"pid":"db4fefd313e404cf193bdf92c48405643b81b0dc","tid":234504,"uid":66557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T14:13:07.000Z","msg":"你好似係想玩zelda嗰個？我都係用xbox elite制，我個receiver重要另外買，印象中冇難度一按即連，但cemu啲制要自己set"},{"pid":"47804692350a7011bd0339f3d7a1901315585f97","tid":234504,"uid":74380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T17:45:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你好似係想玩zelda嗰個？我都係用xbox elite制，我個receiver重要另外買，印象中冇難度一按即連，但cemu啲制要自己set</blockquote><br />\n係呀巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我而家懷疑個手制係懷,聽日去鋪頭換<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fca02b200b35bd93463ed7b2cabed080eb53d96","tid":234504,"uid":74380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl